---
title: Caribbean Tofu & Creamy Coconut Sauce with Bacon Pineapple Slaw & Leafy Rice
description: Give tofu the "Jamaican jerk" treatment and bring the flavours of the Caribbean to your table. For the quintessential experience, serve the seasoned tofu with leafy rice, pineapple slaw and an easy coconut saucy to drizzle over the top.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66a9ba846952abc9873993c5-8d9b3e53.jpeg
